쿠버네티스 서비스 kubernetes service 

1. 개념과 종류
- 쿠버네티스 네트워크가 어렵다.
 
Deployment-definition
/////////////////////
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: webui
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
    app: webui
  template:
    metadata:
      name: nginx-pod
      labels:
        app:webui
    spec:
      container:
      -name : nginx-container

Service-definition
/////////////////////
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: webui-svc
spec:
  clusterIP: 10.96.100.100
  selector:
    app: webui
  ports:
  - protocols: TCP
    port: 80
    targerPort:80

